       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    ARI11103.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA ARI11103.
      *
      *      Perfis
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE ARI11103         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY ARCV1110.
       COPY ARCV1111.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY TGCL1000.
       COPY TGCL2000.
       COPY TGCK0002.
      *
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 WS-PROGNAME  PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARI11103'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CHIERAR1  PIC X(05) VALUE 'AR004'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CURL1  PIC X(05) VALUE 'AR005'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CHIERAR2  PIC X(05) VALUE 'AR004'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CURL2  PIC X(05) VALUE 'AR005'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CHIERAR3  PIC X(05) VALUE 'AR004'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CURL3  PIC X(05) VALUE 'AR005'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CHIERAR4  PIC X(05) VALUE 'AR004'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CURL4  PIC X(05) VALUE 'AR005'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CHIERAR5  PIC X(05) VALUE 'AR004'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CURL5  PIC X(05) VALUE 'AR005'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-CTABELA                   PIC X(05) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CCOD                      PIC X(40) VALUE SPACES.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE ARI11103         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *
           MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
      *    IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
      *       PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
      *          THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
      *    END-IF.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO ARCV1110-MSG.
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT   TO ARCV1111-MSG.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      *
           MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
      *    IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
      *       PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
      *          THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
      *    END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2100-VAL-CAMPOS
                 THRU 2100-VAL-CAMPOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-VAL-CAMPOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-VAL-CAMPOS.
      *
           MOVE '2100-VAL-CAMPOS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
      *    IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
      *       PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
      *          THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
      *    END-IF.
      *

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS AND ARCV1110-CHIERAR1 NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-CHIERAR1         TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE ARCV1110-CHIERAR1            TO WS-CCOD
              PERFORM 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05
                 THRU 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT
              IF NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-S       TO ARCV1111-CHIERAR1-S
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-CAPLIC  TO ARCV1111-CHIERAR1-CAPLIC
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-MSG     TO ARCV1111-CHIERAR1-MSG
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC        TO ARCV1111-XDESCCHIERAR1
              ELSE
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC        TO ARCV1110-XDESCCHIERAR1
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS AND ARCV1110-CURL1 NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-CURL1         TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE ARCV1110-CURL1            TO WS-CCOD
              PERFORM 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05
                 THRU 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT
              IF NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-S       TO ARCV1111-CURL1-S
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-CAPLIC  TO ARCV1111-CURL1-CAPLIC
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-MSG     TO ARCV1111-CURL1-MSG
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC        TO ARCV1111-XDESCCURL1
              ELSE
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC        TO ARCV1110-XDESCCURL1
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS AND ARCV1110-CHIERAR2 NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-CHIERAR2         TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE ARCV1110-CHIERAR2            TO WS-CCOD
              PERFORM 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05
                 THRU 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT
              IF NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-S       TO ARCV1111-CHIERAR2-S
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-CAPLIC  TO ARCV1111-CHIERAR2-CAPLIC
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-MSG     TO ARCV1111-CHIERAR2-MSG
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC        TO ARCV1111-XDESCCHIERAR2
              ELSE
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC        TO ARCV1110-XDESCCHIERAR2
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS AND ARCV1110-CURL2 NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-CURL2         TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE ARCV1110-CURL2            TO WS-CCOD
              PERFORM 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05
                 THRU 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT
              IF NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-S       TO ARCV1111-CURL2-S
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-CAPLIC  TO ARCV1111-CURL2-CAPLIC
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-MSG     TO ARCV1111-CURL2-MSG
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC        TO ARCV1111-XDESCCURL2
              ELSE
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC        TO ARCV1110-XDESCCURL2
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS AND ARCV1110-CHIERAR3 NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-CHIERAR3         TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE ARCV1110-CHIERAR3            TO WS-CCOD
              PERFORM 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05
                 THRU 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT
              IF NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-S       TO ARCV1111-CHIERAR3-S
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-CAPLIC  TO ARCV1111-CHIERAR3-CAPLIC
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-MSG     TO ARCV1111-CHIERAR3-MSG
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC        TO ARCV1111-XDESCCHIERAR3
              ELSE
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC        TO ARCV1110-XDESCCHIERAR3
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS AND ARCV1110-CURL3 NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-CURL3         TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE ARCV1110-CURL3            TO WS-CCOD
              PERFORM 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05
                 THRU 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT
              IF NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-S       TO ARCV1111-CURL3-S
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-CAPLIC  TO ARCV1111-CURL3-CAPLIC
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-MSG     TO ARCV1111-CURL3-MSG
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC        TO ARCV1111-XDESCCURL3
              ELSE
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC        TO ARCV1110-XDESCCURL3
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS AND ARCV1110-CHIERAR4 NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-CHIERAR4         TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE ARCV1110-CHIERAR4            TO WS-CCOD
              PERFORM 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05
                 THRU 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT
              IF NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-S       TO ARCV1111-CHIERAR4-S
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-CAPLIC  TO ARCV1111-CHIERAR4-CAPLIC
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-MSG     TO ARCV1111-CHIERAR4-MSG
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC        TO ARCV1111-XDESCCHIERAR4
              ELSE
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC        TO ARCV1110-XDESCCHIERAR4
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS AND ARCV1110-CURL4 NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-CURL4         TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE ARCV1110-CURL4            TO WS-CCOD
              PERFORM 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05
                 THRU 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT
              IF NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-S       TO ARCV1111-CURL4-S
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-CAPLIC  TO ARCV1111-CURL4-CAPLIC
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-MSG     TO ARCV1111-CURL4-MSG
