      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS AND ARCV1110-CURL5 NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-CURL5         TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE ARCV1110-CURL5            TO WS-CCOD
              PERFORM 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05
                 THRU 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT
              IF NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-S       TO ARCV1111-CURL5-S
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-CAPLIC  TO ARCV1111-CURL5-CAPLIC
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-MSG     TO ARCV1111-CURL5-MSG
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC        TO ARCV1111-XDESCCURL5
              ELSE
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC        TO ARCV1110-XDESCCURL5
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *

       2100-VAL-CAMPOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2200-VAL-TAB-ART05
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-VAL-TAB-ART05.
      *
           MOVE '2200-VAL-TAB-ART05' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID

      *
           INITIALIZE TGCL2000-MSG       REPLACING  NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                               ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.

           MOVE WS-CTABELA                TO TGCL2000-CTABELA
           MOVE WS-CCOD                   TO TGCL2000-CCOD

           PERFORM CALL-TGCP2000
              THRU CALL-TGCP2000-EXIT.

      *    IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
      *       MOVE '2200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
      *       MOVE 'TGCL2000-CCOD       '    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
      *       MOVE  TGCL2000-CCOD            TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
      *       MOVE 'TGCL2000-GDESC      '    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
      *       MOVE  TGCL2000-GDESC           TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
      *       MOVE 'VIAL0002-IND-ERROS  '    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(3)
      *       MOVE  VIAL0002-IND-ERROS       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
      *       PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
      *          THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
      *    END-IF.

       2200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2300-VAL-TAB-OUTRA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2300-VAL-TAB-OUTRA.
      *
           MOVE '2300-VAL-TAB-OUTRA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID

           INITIALIZE TGCL1000-MSG       REPLACING  NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                               ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.

           MOVE WS-CTABELA                TO TGCL1000-CTABELA
           MOVE WS-CCOD                   TO TGCL1000-CCOD

           PERFORM CALL-TGCP1000
              THRU CALL-TGCP1000-EXIT.

      *    IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
      *       MOVE '2300-VAL-TAB-OUTRA-EXIT' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
      *       MOVE 'TGCL1000-CCOD       '    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
      *       MOVE  TGCL1000-CCOD            TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
